---
layout: base.njk
current: songs
permalink: /songs/
title: Songs That Found Me at the Right Time
description: "Artists share the songs that found them at the right time, and the stories behind why those songs carried them through."
ogType: website
---
{#
  Editorial intro is mirrored from content/pages/songs.json (the CMS-editable
  source of record). Kept inline here too so the page is never empty if the
  JSON is unavailable at build. Keep the two in sync when editing copy.
#}
{% set songsIntro = "Music has been clinically proven to have a positive impact on mental health. The right song can affect our psychobiological stress system and create feelings of motivation, happiness and relaxation. In this series, artists share the songs that found them at the right time, and the stories behind why they matter." %}

<style>
  .songs-page { padding-block: var(--space-xl); }
  .songs-head { max-width: var(--maxw-prose); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
  .songs-head h1 { font-size: var(--fs-title); line-height: var(--lh-tight); margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm); }
  .songs-intro { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: var(--lh-base); color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; }

  .songs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .song-card { display: flex; }
  .song-card__link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }
  .song-card__link:hover,
  .song-card__link:focus-visible {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .song-card__media {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .song-card__media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .song-card__play {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .song-card__play svg {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5));
    opacity: 0.92;
  }
  .song-card__body { padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md) var(--space-md); }
  .song-card__artist {
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .song-card__title {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    margin: var(--space-3xs) 0 0;
  }
  .song-card--featured .song-card__link { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .songs-label {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    font-size: var(--fs-tiny);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
  }
  .songs-section + .songs-section { margin-top: var(--space-xl); }
</style>

<div class="container songs-page">
  <header class="songs-head">
    <p class="songs-label">Series</p>
    <h1>Songs That Found Me at the Right Time</h1>
    <p class="songs-intro">{{ songsIntro }}</p>
  </header>

  {% set featured = songs | selectattr("featured") | list %}
  {% set rest = songs | rejectattr("featured") | list %}

  {% if featured.length %}
  <section class="songs-section" aria-label="Featured">
    <ul class="songs-grid">
      {% for s in featured %}
        <li class="song-card song-card--featured">
          <a class="song-card__link" href="{{ s.url }}">
            <span class="song-card__media">
              {% if s.thumbnail %}<img src="{{ s.thumbnail | img }}" alt="{{ s.title }}"{% if s.dims %} width="{{ s.dims.width }}" height="{{ s.dims.height }}"{% endif %} loading="lazy" decoding="async" />{% endif %}
              <span class="song-card__play" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
              </span>
            </span>
            <span class="song-card__body">
              <p class="song-card__artist">{{ s.artist }}</p>
              {% if s.song_title %}<p class="song-card__title">{{ s.song_title }}</p>{% endif %}
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% if rest.length %}
  <section class="songs-section" aria-label="More songs">
    {% if featured.length %}<p class="songs-label">More from the series</p>{% endif %}
    <ul class="songs-grid">
      {% for s in rest %}
        <li class="song-card">
          <a class="song-card__link" href="{{ s.url }}">
            <span class="song-card__media">
              {% if s.thumbnail %}<img src="{{ s.thumbnail | img }}" alt="{{ s.title }}"{% if s.dims %} width="{{ s.dims.width }}" height="{{ s.dims.height }}"{% endif %} loading="lazy" decoding="async" />{% endif %}
              <span class="song-card__play" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
              </span>
            </span>
            <span class="song-card__body">
              <p class="song-card__artist">{{ s.artist }}</p>
              {% if s.song_title %}<p class="song-card__title">{{ s.song_title }}</p>{% endif %}
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
  {% endif %}
</div>
